org.modelio.vcore.smkernel

Interface IRepositoryObject


  • public interface IRepositoryObject
    Repository object interface.

    Called by the meta object (IMetaOf) to load parts of a SmObjectImpl when required.
    Notified for each SmObjectImpl modification.
